Class DynamicIntegerDithering

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.dither.development.DynamicIntegerDithering
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DitherHolder, DitheringAlgorithm
    Deprecated. 
    Should not be used in real environments!

    @LegacyApi(since="1.2.0")
 @Deprecated
public class DynamicIntegerDithering
extends java.lang.Object
implements DitherHolder
    A custom approach which uses FilterLite along a memory cached lookup table full of already dithered values. Uses integers which are must faster, but uses an extreme amount of memory. (Dynamic Programming)
